---
layout: base.njk
title: Insights
description: Vendor-neutral analysis of AI tools, implementation strategies, and industry shifts. Written by practitioners, not pundits.
permalink: /insights/
---

<header class="listing-header">
    <h1>Insights</h1>
    <p>Vendor-neutral analysis of AI tools, implementation strategies, and what actually matters for your business.</p>
</header>

<ul class="post-list">
{% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li class="post-item">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            {% if post.data.category %}<div class="post-category">{{ post.data.category }}</div>{% endif %}
            <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description or post.templateContent | excerpt }}</p>
            <span class="post-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}{% if post.data.readTime %} &middot; {{ post.data.readTime }} min read{% endif %}</span>
        </a>
    </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>

{% if collections.posts.length == 0 %}
<div style="max-width: 740px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 2rem; color: #999; text-align: center;">
    <p>New content coming soon. <a href="{{ site.url }}/#contact" style="color: var(--sage);">Get in touch</a> if you have questions now.</p>
</div>
{% endif %}
